      <title>普拉博沃希望前银行家担任印度尼西亚财政部长一职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/prabowo-eyes-former-bankers-for-indonesia-finance-minister-role</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚的普拉博沃·苏比安托(Prabowo Subianto)将目光投向了前银行家，以寻找他的财政部长，因为他正在寻找能够为他的竞选承诺获得资金，同时坚持财政审慎的技术官僚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/prabowo-eyes-former-bankers-for-indonesia-finance-minister-role</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉誓言对新威胁中的圭亚那边境索赔做出回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/venezuela-vows-response-to-guyana-border-claim-in-latest-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总统伊尔法安·阿里坚称该国的合法边界于 1899 年确定并包括被称为埃塞奎博的领土后，委内瑞拉誓言将对圭亚那的“严重侵犯行为”做出“相应”反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/venezuela-vows-response-to-guyana-border-claim-in-latest-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 22:43:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃伦呼吁对大型科技公司进军人工智能领域设置新限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/warren-calls-for-new-limits-on-big-tech-s-push-into-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员伊丽莎白·沃伦 (Elizabeth Warren) 呼吁对主要云提供商微软公司 (Microsoft Corp.)、亚马逊公司 (Amazon.com Inc.) 和 Alphabet Inc. 实施新的限制，禁止它们开发一些最有前途的人工智能技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/warren-calls-for-new-limits-on-big-tech-s-push-into-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 22:17:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法尼·威利斯不当行为案中的“明星证人”在证人席上动摇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/-star-witness-in-fani-willis-misconduct-case-falters-on-stand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在富尔顿县地方检察官法尼·威利斯的不当行为听证会上，这位著名的明星证人在作证时支吾其词，讲述她与领导针对唐纳德·特朗普案件的特别检察官的恋情是何时开始的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/-star-witness-in-fani-willis-misconduct-case-falters-on-stand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 22:10:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国表示，四分之一的加沙人现在距离饥荒“仅一步之遥”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/one-in-four-gazans-are-now-one-step-away-from-famine-un-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国警告说，加沙地带四分之一的人距离经历饥荒“仅一步之遥”，并表示，随着人道主义机构报告向饱受战争蹂躏的地区运送援助遇到困难，情况将进一步恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/one-in-four-gazans-are-now-one-step-away-from-famine-un-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 21:54:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
