    <item>
      <title>由于阿根廷各省的抵制，米莱的大胆法令摇摇欲坠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/milei-s-december-decree-teeters-as-argentina-provinces-resist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院对哈维尔·米莱总统的全面法令的反对声音越来越大，这使得该法令在下周例行会议开始时面临被推翻的风险，从而危及他最初的经济休克疗法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/milei-s-december-decree-teeters-as-argentina-provinces-resist</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 16:41:09 GMT</pubDate>
